Set Sail for Adventure with Key West Promotions!
Established in October 2002, Key West Promotions has become a leading source of unforgettable experiences for island visitors. Our journey began with the iconic Key West Pub Crawl™, a perennial favorite that's entertained over 250,000 guests and counting!
Over the years, we've expanded our offerings to cater to diverse interests. From spooky ghost tours and delectable culinary adventures to immersive history and cultural explorations, we have something for everyone. Now, get ready to set sail on paradise with our all-new Tiki Bar Boat Tours!
At Key West Promotions, we're passionate about creating entertaining experiences that offer exceptional value. We go the extra mile to ensure a personalized touch on every tour. Our team of highly trained guides prioritizes great customer service and guest safety, ensuring you have a worry-free adventure.
Fully licensed and insured, Key West Promotions is your trusted partner for exploring the magic of Key West. Let's create memories that last a lifetime!
Cruise Ship Tours
Are you taking a cruise that visits Key West? We specialize in cruise  ship  passenger tours where we'll pick you up right from the cruise ship pier to begin the tour. Each of our tours is available directly from  your cruise line. They can be purchased in advance on each line's website or on board from the Shore Excursion Desk.
